### 3. Sum of an Array

Calculating the sum of all elements in an array using recursion.

```java
public class ArraySum {

    public static int sum(int[] arr, int n) {
        if (n <= 0) return 0; // Base case
        return arr[n - 1] + sum(arr, n - 1); // Recursive call
    }

