- **F(4) = F(3) + F(2) = 2 + 1 = 3**
- **F(5) = F(4) + F(3) = 3 + 2 = 5**
- **F(6) = F(5) + F(4) = 5 + 3 = 8**
- **F(7) = F(6) + F(5) = 8 + 5 = 13**
- **F(8) = F(7) + F(6) = 13 + 8 = 21**

